{"tid":358998,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"誰人才是你們心目中的千古一帝呢?","createTime":"2017-08-14T06:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T07:24:47.000Z","uid":30081,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d263180c8013cc7d1e350de5b0ba6b0cae762bf6","tid":358998,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"引用一下毛生的名句<br />\n<br />\n「江山如此多嬌，引無數英雄競折腰。 <br />\n惜秦皇漢武，略輸文采；唐宗宋祖，稍遜風騷。 <br />\n一代天驕，成吉思汗，只識彎弓射大雕。 <br />\n俱往矣，數風流人物，還看今朝。 」<br />\n<br />\n芸芸眾多皇帝, 誰才是你所想的千古一帝呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就認為係漢光武"},{"pid":"05139c43b9831cac289fa445de1b632c40cfb992","tid":358998,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:44:04.000Z","msg":"宋仁宗 漢文帝"},{"pid":"81046249fa18ba46b1f05bb866c8f21414847337","tid":358998,"uid":53794,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:51:50.000Z","msg":"老毛"},{"pid":"fde04d32758909b9097229158530e44b7f293df9","tid":358998,"uid":90704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"李世民<br />\n佢當時個社會好似理想啲"},{"pid":"b902bb2c40aa2d1b1fbf707a2df98e82bae8ef64","tid":358998,"uid":3422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"計唔計外國先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71b6018c3db8b49d6c99f070528968be5583feb","tid":358998,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"腓特烈"},{"pid":"0e431456953550faa62be2b0ac4c55a13acea497","tid":358998,"uid":126933,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"秦始皇"},{"pid":"ba15bb72e9de13eb239763731d6928a43185cea7","tid":358998,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:43:41.000Z","msg":"晉惠帝"},{"pid":"9bc313577b48ef47f7eeec225539dd6b29442121","tid":358998,"uid":2211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:44:20.000Z","msg":